      <title>中国钢铁产量将突破北京限制，三年来首次增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-s-steel-output-set-to-bust-cap-by-rising-for-first-time-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国钢铁产量有望实现三年来首次年度增长，因为经济问题优先于减少高污染行业排放的需要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-s-steel-output-set-to-bust-cap-by-rising-for-first-time-in-three-years</guid>
